NMB RT-101 ANSI

Manufacturer: NMB

Switches: Hi-Tek Series 725 “Space Invaders” “Two-eye white” Linear (Lubed)

Date: ~1989

Origin: A confusing classification system of keyboards from NMB. Uses a very interesting series of switches (dubbed the Space Invaders by the Mechanical Keyboards community due to their distinctive shape).

PS/2 protocol so no conversion necessary. However it could potentially use some minor cleaning.
